content.p: The School of Economics awards the following prizes to undergraduate students on an annual basis: 2015 School Prizes for Outstanding Performance in Undergraduate Studies. 2016 School Prize for Outstanding Achievement. 2017 School Prize for Outstanding Achievement. 2017 School Prize for Outstanding Performance in Undergraduate. 2018 School Prize for Outstanding Achievement. 2018 School Prize for Overall Performance in Undergraduate. telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8253 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8019
